00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,290
I'm heart-broken.

299
00:17:03,450 --> 00:17:05,290
I need your warm consolation.

300
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,660
Yun Shu is here.

301
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,860
Hello.

302
00:17:19,370 --> 00:17:20,340
Pregnant?

303
00:17:20,890 --> 00:17:23,280
My sis knew that just now.

304
00:17:23,370 --> 00:17:24,250
But she said she didn't want to

305
00:17:24,370 --> 00:17:26,100
tell you that.

306
00:17:26,190 --> 00:17:27,440
But I think you should.

307
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:29,500
But I think it's about you two.

308
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:30,480
So.

309
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:31,890
So you have the right to know.

310
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,290
Just extend your thanks by words.

311
00:17:39,390 --> 00:17:40,310
Thank you, sis-in-law.

312
00:17:40,390 --> 00:17:41,480
You're my saviour.

313
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:43,150
I've never seen my sis

314
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:45,340
act this way since my childhood.

315
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,620
So.

316
00:17:51,170 --> 00:17:53,340
So where is he now?

317
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,430
He must go to change his clothes

318
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:57,040
then he'll rush to your sis.

319
00:17:58,970 --> 00:18:01,300
From now on, we're a family.

320
00:18:01,390 --> 00:18:02,510
I'm going to find Yun Lan.

321
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:04,500
Nian Nian.

322
00:18:04,590 --> 00:18:06,110
Take good care of my sis-in-law.

323
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,820
Or I'll get you punished.

324
00:18:14,390 --> 00:18:15,940
Silly boy!

325
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:18,690
So.

326
00:18:19,970 --> 00:18:22,330
I'm the younger sis-in-law or

327
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:23,690
elder sis-in-law?

328
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:26,090
You're the elder sis-in-law of course.

329
00:18:28,990 --> 00:18:29,870
Great.

330
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:54,710
Lan,

331
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:55,910
Come to the doorway.

332
00:18:55,990 --> 00:18:57,010
Lu Yu is waiting for you.

333
00:18:57,090 --> 00:18:58,340
All the people are watching.

334
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:06,880
What's the matter?

335
00:19:06,970 --> 00:19:08,560
Can you think it over
before you do something?

336
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,940
It's Lu Yun. The real Lu Yu.

337
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:11,640
Yun Shu told me everything.

338
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:14,080
I don't know what you're talking about.

339
00:19:14,170 --> 00:19:15,310
He's so handsome.

340
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,620
It's him.

341
00:19:34,890 --> 00:19:36,160
Marry me.

342
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:41,160
Come on, give me a break.

343
00:19:41,250 --> 00:19:42,630
I love you. I want to marry you.

344
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:44,440
You think I'm making a scene?

345
00:19:48,170 --> 00:19:49,510
Let's go somewhere else.

346
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,780
Yun Lan, I love you.

347
00:19:51,390 --> 00:19:53,590
I imagined our future life,
living together

348
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,180
many times.

349
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:57,630
I just have no guts
to tell you my feelings.

350
00:19:57,710 --> 00:19:59,030
I was afraid that you would reject me.

351
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:02,140
I was afraid that you'd run away

352
00:20:02,290 --> 00:20:03,570
if I proposed to you.

353
00:20:04,450 --> 00:20:06,440
When I knew you were pregnant,

354
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:07,680
I just want to marry you.

355
00:20:07,770 --> 00:20:08,500
It's the only idea in my mind

356
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:10,160
I want to marry you.

357
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:11,480
Even if it means getting rejected
by you

358
00:20:12,050 --> 00:20:13,840
or scaring you away,

359
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:16,430
I will keep proposing

360
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:17,910
till you say yes.

361
00:20:26,110 --> 00:20:27,200
Stand up first.

362
00:20:27,290 --> 00:20:28,220
Say Yes first.

363
00:20:37,190 --> 00:20:38,080
What's wrong with you?

364
00:20:38,170 --> 00:20:38,560
I...

365
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,950
I feel unwell.

366
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:40,630
Oh, no.

367
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,910
What?

368
00:20:42,650 --> 00:20:43,290
My tummy hurts.

369
00:20:43,370 --> 00:20:44,420
Tummy hurts?

370
00:20:45,970 --> 00:20:46,760
Are you OK?

371
00:20:46,850 --> 00:20:48,140
I will take you to the hospital.

372
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:49,840
Slow down.

373
00:20:50,190 --> 00:20:51,480
They are well matched.

374
00:20:51,570 --> 00:20:52,510
Yes.

375
00:20:53,290 --> 00:20:54,770
So sweet.

376
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:57,640
Are you feeling unwell?

377
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:04,990
I'm OK.

378
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:06,110
I was only fooling you.

379
00:21:08,090 --> 00:21:09,040
Come on.

380
00:21:09,890 --> 00:21:11,370
How could you kid this thing?

381
00:21:12,570 --> 00:21:14,040
You made me angry.

382
00:21:14,770 --> 00:21:16,240
Everybody's watching.

383
00:21:16,490 --> 00:21:17,690
I feel so embarrassed.

384
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,510
Come on.

385
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:23,240
They envied us.

386
00:21:23,990 --> 00:21:25,610
Can you be low profile in the future?

387
00:21:26,170 --> 00:21:27,830
I don't want people to
talk about me every day.

388
00:21:28,320 --> 00:21:29,590
Yes, Mummy.

389
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:34,300
Do you want to eat anything?

390
00:21:34,390 --> 00:21:36,010
I heard that pregnant
women have no appetite,

391
00:21:36,090 --> 00:21:38,010
so I prepared plum and crataegus for you.

392
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:39,440
I don't want to eat anything sour.

393
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:41,170
So you want to eat something spicy?

394
00:21:41,360 --> 00:21:43,040
Maybe we'll have a sweet daughter.

395
00:21:43,120 --> 00:21:43,750
Great.

396
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:44,230
I like daughters.

397
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:45,410
Can you shut up?

398
00:21:49,370 --> 00:21:51,710
Let me finish my words.

399
00:21:53,970 --> 00:21:56,160
You accepted my proposal, did you?

400
00:21:56,250 --> 00:21:57,140
No.

401
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,890
You have a three-month probation.

402
00:22:05,990 --> 00:22:07,170
It depends.

403
00:22:09,190 --> 00:22:10,080
Okay.

404
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,110
Alright, how about I

405
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,560
propose to you every day?

406
00:22:14,650 --> 00:22:15,640
Slow down.

407
00:22:15,910 --> 00:22:17,460
Are you a fool?

408
00:22:19,110 --> 00:22:20,240
Slow down.

409
00:22:35,570 --> 00:22:38,610
[Volunteer recruitment]

410
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:54,090
I'll go for you in Africa.

411
00:22:54,390 --> 00:22:55,510
Wait and see.

412
00:23:10,770 --> 00:23:12,550
Can you change

413
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:14,230
your short temper?

414
00:23:17,170 --> 00:23:19,340
No, I can. So what?

415
00:23:20,320 --> 00:23:21,770
What can I do?

416
00:23:21,890 --> 00:23:23,390
I can only go to pick you up.

417
00:24:00,370 --> 00:24:01,590
Slow down, grandpa.

418
00:24:07,300 --> 00:24:10,170
Are you two ready?

419
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,940
Wait a second. We'll be right here.

420
00:24:17,690 --> 00:24:18,560
How is it?

421
00:24:18,650 --> 00:24:19,910
Are you ready?

422
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,790
Of course.

423
00:24:22,770 --> 00:24:23,710
Look.

424
00:24:23,800 --> 00:24:25,890
What are they talking about?

425
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,830
Come on.

426
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:30,360
He's talking with Lu Yu.

427
00:24:31,170 --> 00:24:32,110
Yun Lan.

428
00:24:32,890 --> 00:24:34,440
Lu Yu and Si Nian

429
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:36,590
seem to be

430
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:38,730
totally different types of people

431
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:40,890
but they're alike deep down inside.

432
00:24:41,490 --> 00:24:45,040
Lu Yu seems to be cynical.

433
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:46,200
Si Nian seems to be

434
00:24:46,290 --> 00:24:47,690
aloof,

435
00:24:48,250 --> 00:24:49,360
but they are both

436
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:51,230
kind

437
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:53,480
and reliable.

438
00:24:59,490 --> 00:25:00,940
I mean,

439
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:02,690
are you ready to be a dad?

440
00:25:04,370 --> 00:25:05,620
Of course.

441
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:08,280
The crib, the stroller,

442
00:25:08,370 --> 00:25:09,910
the diapers, the pacifier,

443
00:25:09,990 --> 00:25:10,870
the urinal and the nanny are all ready.

444
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:12,840
The baby's name remains unknown.

445
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:14,640
Save it.

446
00:25:15,770 --> 00:25:17,130
You know what I mean.

447
00:25:19,770 --> 00:25:21,760
To be honest,

448
00:25:22,390 --> 00:25:23,270
I am not yet ready.

449
00:25:23,590 --> 00:25:26,360
I don't know what I should do.

450
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,270
I just know

451
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:33,010
I love Yun Lan.

452
00:25:33,090 --> 00:25:36,520
She's a woman with
little sense of security.

453
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,590
I want to give her a family.

454
00:25:45,090 --> 00:25:46,360
Good for you.

455
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,480
Your words show that you're ready now.

456
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:52,080
Come on.

457
00:25:52,170 --> 00:25:53,300
Call me bro-in-law, come on.

458
00:25:53,390 --> 00:25:54,510
Come on, for God's sake.

459
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:56,110
Did Yun Lan say Yes?

460
00:25:56,190 --> 00:25:58,010
What are you ducking?

461
00:25:58,170 --> 00:25:59,830
Come on. Hurry up.

462
00:26:00,300 --> 00:26:01,690
We'll be right here.

463
00:26:03,890 --> 00:26:04,820
Lan.

464
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,190
What's your test for Lu Yun?

465
00:26:11,570 --> 00:26:13,520
I didn't mean to test him.

466
00:26:14,090 --> 00:26:15,960
I just have no confidence in myself.

467
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:18,020
I'm not sure whether

468
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:20,810
I can be a good wife and

469
00:26:20,900 --> 00:26:22,140
a good mother.

470
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,540
I believe she'll make

471
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:25,660
a good mother

472
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:27,410
and a good wife.

473
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,110
Let's get it started.

474
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:36,670
Brother-in-law.

475
00:26:41,390 --> 00:26:42,110
Kids,

476
00:26:42,190 --> 00:26:43,950
remember my words.

477
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,640
In family,

478
00:26:46,520 --> 00:26:47,630
love

479
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:49,110
reigns.

480
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,120
Go.

481
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:11,320
♫ You're a familiar stranger ♫

482
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:13,420
♫ Who keeps appearing before me ♫

483
00:27:12,890 --> 00:27:13,770
Look,

484
00:27:14,450 --> 00:27:15,800
♫ You're clumsy yet kind ♫

485
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:18,320
♫ Ringing the bell in my heart ♫

486
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:22,930
♫ You predict and plan, but you can't
solve the problem called love ♫

487
00:27:23,250 --> 00:27:27,120
♫ Let me tell you, just hold my hand ♫

488
00:27:28,090 --> 00:27:32,320
♫ Looking up, I see
the most perfect you ♫

489
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:35,800
♫ Close your eyes and feel me out,
the plain girl ♫

490
00:27:51,320 --> 00:27:52,280
it's cold.

491
00:27:52,370 --> 00:27:53,840
Cover your knees.

492
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:54,430
OK,

493
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:57,080
Grandpa, it's windy here.

494
00:27:57,170 --> 00:27:59,160
Keep yourself warm.

495
00:27:59,250 --> 00:28:00,130
Yun Shu,

496
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:03,010
I'd like to thank you.

497
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:07,290
You made Si Nian warm-hearted.

498
00:28:11,170 --> 00:28:12,080
Sit down.

499
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:20,060
Actually, I had long known

500
00:28:20,770 --> 00:28:22,610
your contract.

501
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:29,490
Grandpa, don't think too much.

502
00:28:29,570 --> 00:28:30,960
Si Nian and I...

503
00:28:31,050 --> 00:28:31,750
No need to explain.

504
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:33,430
I know you did that

505
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:36,150
for me.

506
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,280
Grandpa,

507
00:28:38,100 --> 00:28:39,690
That's not true.

508
00:28:40,170 --> 00:28:42,000
Yun Shu and I

509
00:28:42,090 --> 00:28:43,840
are meant to be.

510
00:28:44,050 --> 00:28:47,120
So, when did you
start to love each other?

511
00:28:49,790 --> 00:28:51,740
When I first met him,

512
00:28:52,190 --> 00:28:53,230
I thought I wouldn't see

513
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:55,410
him any more.

514
00:28:56,170 --> 00:28:57,440
Make a Latte for me

515
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,570
according to what I wrote.

516
00:28:58,790 --> 00:29:00,310
Black coffee is classic.

517
00:29:00,390 --> 00:29:01,480
Fastidious?

518
00:29:02,590 --> 00:29:03,580
Dear students,

519
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:04,510
I'm Zhang Si Nian.

520
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:06,280
Starting today, I'll be in charge

521
00:29:06,370 --> 00:29:08,360
of the Mathematical Statistics course.

522
00:29:08,450 --> 00:29:09,810
The whole picture is
nothing but stupid errors.

523
00:29:09,900 --> 00:29:11,150
In the future,

524
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:12,430
you can't avoid him.

525
00:29:12,520 --> 00:29:14,110
Impossible!

526
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,080
Mr Zhang.

527
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:16,830
You've forfeited your chance

528
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:17,750
at your thesis defence.

529
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:18,890
Because you're late.

530
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:23,880
♫ Turning off the lights
in search of its trace ♫

531
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:20,560
You're really the most fastidious teacher

532
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:22,240
I've ever seen.

533
00:29:23,300 --> 00:29:24,510
I don't care whether
you have time or not.

534
00:29:24,590 --> 00:29:26,030
If you don't go with me today,

535
00:29:24,930 --> 00:29:29,770
♫ I walk steadily
on the path beneath my feet ♫

536
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:26,960
I won't get in your car.

537
00:29:27,050 --> 00:29:28,200
I think I have figured it out.

538
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:29,290
You may have been fooled.

539
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:31,230
He's my cousin.

540
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:36,460
♫ I hear someone asking,
are you still here? ♫

541
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,590
How could he fool me?

542
00:29:34,990 --> 00:29:36,080
Can you do me a favour?

543
00:29:36,170 --> 00:29:36,800
Sure.

544
00:29:36,890 --> 00:29:37,770
Be my girlfriend.

545
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:42,360
♫ The kind person replies,
I've always been here ♫

546
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:40,020
You can hold my hands.

547
00:29:40,990 --> 00:29:41,830
One month.

548
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:42,960
Marriage?

549
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:46,050
♫ This love cuts through the crowd
in search of me ♫

550
00:29:43,770 --> 00:29:45,220
