557
00:29:51,150 --> 00:29:52,030
Mr Zhang,

558
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:53,750
you've long set the trap?

559
00:29:52,570 --> 00:29:53,890
♫ Each and every moment ♫

560
00:29:53,840 --> 00:29:55,490
It is not a marriage
in the traditional sense,

561
00:29:55,160 --> 00:30:00,270
♫ If I missed out, I will meet you again
in another lifetime ♫

562
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,600
while it's a kind of

563
00:29:56,840 --> 00:29:57,560
contractual relationship.

564
00:29:57,650 --> 00:29:59,210
The marriage you mean is more like

565
00:29:59,300 --> 00:30:01,000
a sort of cooperation.

566
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:07,260
♫ I recognise your eyes,
a secret that belongs to me ♫

567
00:30:01,090 --> 00:30:02,410
You're having a hard time.

568
00:30:02,500 --> 00:30:03,100
No.

569
00:30:03,190 --> 00:30:04,070
I'm not.

570
00:30:04,050 --> 00:30:06,250
[Mathematics as I Know It]

571
00:30:04,290 --> 00:30:05,170
Yun Shu,

572
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,490
I remember I told you the
morning before yesterday.

573
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:09,340
Don't go to school.

574
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:10,310
Don't let more people

575
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:11,560
know about our relationship.

576
00:30:12,560 --> 00:30:14,310
Do you look down on me?

577
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:16,950
You think I'm

578
00:30:17,040 --> 00:30:18,440
a useless person?

579
00:30:19,990 --> 00:30:20,800
Who are you?

580
00:30:20,890 --> 00:30:21,760
I'm Zhang Si Nian.

581
00:30:21,850 --> 00:30:22,880
I'm her husband.

582
00:30:22,970 --> 00:30:23,860
We're married.

583
00:30:23,950 --> 00:30:25,240
From today on,

